d":"42b76d385d64d4073dd113d286d323df9c7e9d9a","tid":30694,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有D仆街重要在住宅樓下，晨咁草係度響按！<br />\n正仆街！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今朝畀架大車嘈醒，仲以為自己部電話做乜突然震得咁勁，就爆炸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64068aadd2f4ec140ec9707a6a1d045abf7a0df","tid":30694,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:11:29.000Z","msg":"你又岩  響完會唔塞咩   好撚嘈"},{"pid":"fd32622b6df8219a829350f95a2b706cbbb2687a","tid":30694,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:12:00.000Z","msg":"係長響先on9<br />\n佢係塞未走得你響黎把撚"},{"pid":"de929492c8a9692e97d085b80a8b9ba6dde337e6","tid":30694,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:12:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實呠完好撚有成就感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 成日呠d亂咁過馬路既廢老 有次有個比我長呠完仲口up up  再呠多兩下 嚇到佢仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你要用呢d黎拎成就感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人報警就有排煩，之前有人呠鳩個癈老，癈老仆街入左院，司機比後車同路人一齊指証，跟手不正確嚮號同危駕罪成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"d21ff0ea3101f415e0d1172c58ee653c450b0b9b","tid":30694,"uid":38738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:17:18.000Z","msg":"其實有車唔係大撚曬<br />\n佢響只不過代表佢冇耐性<br />\n<br />\nBtw，同意響都多鳩餘，塞車響撚完都係塞<br />\n同埋其實係車入面都好撚嘈"},{"pid":"05c01e2ad948cd891b4ca7c804b5321a1f244232","tid":30694,"uid":13675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:22:01.000Z","msg":"認真 早十年八年 <br />\n我每次番大陸都好憎d喇叭撚<br />\n大陸人係又響唔係又響<br />\n反而香港真係少見<br />\n<br />\n但近年<br />\n我係以為自己番咗大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7e4e13e11f3cc2b7626eca5883aec6aecad798","tid":30694,"uid":17235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:15:05.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但屌你老味人手filter"},{"pid":"10d04917002cf739584dbf74164ae8adb8f85529","tid":30694,"uid":7980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:52:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但屌你老味人手filter</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細佬知錯"},{"pid":"7a834c8f20f968d5e9461bcfb542c2a7f27ddb1c","tid":30694,"uid":2090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實呠完好撚有成就感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 成日呠d亂咁過馬路既廢老 有次有個比我長呠完仲口up up  再呠多兩下 嚇到佢仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你要用呢d黎拎成就感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人報警就有排煩，之前有人呠鳩個癈老，癈老仆街入左院，司機比後車同路人一齊指証，跟手不正確嚮號同危駕罪成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢亂過馬路喎<br />\n佢紅公仔喎<br />\n佢好撚危險喎<br />\n佢行得好慢喎<br />\n我覺得有即時危險喎<br />\n容乜易我後面收唔切架<br />\n我提下佢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁都不正確響號咁我冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d1f324afd100b9043a2e3361d620ba1994d9be","tid":30694,"uid":29592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實呠完好撚有成就